<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Your Petrol Bunk</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">

    <style>

        /* styles.css */


        /* Reset some default styles */

        body, h1, h2, h3, p, ul, li {

            margin: 0;

            padding: 0;

        }


        body {

            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;

        }


        /* Header styles */

        header {

            background-color: #333;

            color: #fff;

        }


        header .container {

            display: flex;

            justify-content: space-between;

            align-items: center;

            padding: 20px;

        }


        header h1 {

            font-size: 24px;

        }


        header ul {

            list-style: none;

            display: flex;

        }


        header ul li {

            margin-right: 20px;

        }


        header ul li a {

            text-decoration: none;

            color: #fff;

        }


        .hero {

            background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/3602009/pexels-photo-3602009.jpeg'); /* Updated background image URL */

            background-size: cover;

            background-position: center;

            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 200px 0; /* Increased padding for a taller background */
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Service features in a row */
        .services .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: flex-start;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .feature {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 300px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            position: relative; /* Added for tooltip positioning */
        }

        .feature img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .feature h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        /* Tooltip styles */
        .tooltip {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            z-index: 1;
            bottom: 100%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 220px;
            text-align: center;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

        /* Show tooltip on hover */
        .feature:hover .tooltip {
            display: block;
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-10px);
        }

        /* About section styles */
        .about {
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .about h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* Contact section styles */
        .contact {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .contact h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .contact address {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        /* ... Rest of the styles ... */
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Your Petrol Bunk</h1>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Welcome to Our Petrol Bunk</h2>
            <p>Providing high-quality fuel and services since 19XX.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="service-img">
                    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/8931961/pexels-photo-8931961.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="Unleaded Petrol">
                    <h3>Unleaded Petrol</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <p>We offer high-quality unleaded petrol for your vehicles.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="service-img">
                    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/372810/pexels-photo-372810.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="Car Wash">
                    <h3>Car Wash</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <p>Get your car washed while refueling for a clean ride.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="service-img">
                    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/12377480/pexels-photo-12377480.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="Diesel">
                    <h3>Diesel</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <p>We provide diesel for trucks and diesel-powered vehicles.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="service-img">
                    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5699376/pexels-photo-5699376.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="ATM">
                    <h3>ATM</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <p>Conveniently access cash from our on-site ATM.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>At Your Petrol Bunk, we're more than just a fuel station; we're your trusted partner on the road. Our commitment to quality is reflected in every drop of fuel we provide, ensuring your vehicle performs at its best mile after mile. Whether you're looking for unleaded petrol, diesel, or a quick car 
wash, we've got you covered. Our mission is to fuel your journey while delivering top-notch service with a smile. Conveniently located at 123 Main Street, we're your pit stop for premium fuel and so much more. Join us on the road to excellence and experience the difference at Your Petrol Bunk â€“ where every drop counts, and your satisfaction is our priority</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <address>
                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Main Street, City, ZIP Code</p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@yourpetrolbunk.com</p>
            </address>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2023 Your Petrol Bunk. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <!-- ... Rest of the page (same as before) ... -->

</body>
</html>



















